{
  "id": "adv_event_2512_01_03",
  "title": "聖夜の\n発明品",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルとファンの想いが相乗効果となって\nライブ会場に膨大なエネルギーを生み出していた……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 8.2721768379,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "そのエネルギーを使えば\n貴方達は元の世界に帰れるかもしれないのね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.4666666667,
      "endTime": 13.804535166600001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lala",
      "speakerName": "ララ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lala.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-lala001.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　だから、ライブ中にエネルギーを回収出来る\nように、みんなの衣装を改造させてもらえないかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.9962355932,
      "endTime": 21.4829030355,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "私達の衣装を！？　あなた達の言ってることは\n分かるけど、いつも使ってる衣装はちょっと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.6962361019,
      "endTime": 28.964808241600004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "確かにそうですよね。……あ、そうだ！　ちょうど\n今作ってるクリスマス衣装を改造するのはどうですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.1629034043,
      "endTime": 37.737869644300005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "それなら可能かもしれないわね\nデザインはまだ確定していなかったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.929570071,
      "endTime": 43.6142412822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-kyui001.m4a",
      "text": "お願い、瑠依さん。これは元の世界に帰るために\n必要なの。協力してくれないかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.829570071,
      "endTime": 50.7229052226,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "……分かったわ。そのかわり、あなた達には\nライブの準備を手伝ってもらってもいいかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.9295718511,
      "endTime": 57.0392089208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yami",
      "speakerName": "金色の闇",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yami.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-yami001.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました\n私達に出来ることなら、なんでも言って下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.2295718511,
      "endTime": 62.766666666700004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "それなら、せっかくだから、モモさん達も衣装を着て\n一緒にステージに立ちませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.0295675277,
      "endTime": 69.499567604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-kyui002.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ！？\n私達がステージで歌うなんて無理よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.6962341944,
      "endTime": 73.8362357774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yami",
      "speakerName": "金色の闇",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yami.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-yami002.m4a",
      "text": "効率はいいですね。改造衣装を着た人の数が多いほど\nエネルギーを早く回収出来ます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.0295690535,
      "endTime": 81.24958295789999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "momo",
      "speakerName": "モモ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-momo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-momo001.m4a",
      "text": "それに、サプライズゲストでライブが盛り上がれば\nより多くのエネルギーが発生するかもしれないですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.4629161196,
      "endTime": 88.54292062089999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "つまり、大量のエネルギーを一気に集めるには\nあなた達もステージに立った方がいいということね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.7295873639,
      "endTime": 95.8300634381,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lala",
      "speakerName": "ララ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lala.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-lala002.m4a",
      "text": "何より、みんなで歌った方が楽しいよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.0295873639,
      "endTime": 99.6495903965,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-kyui003.m4a",
      "text": "……仕方ないわね。これも元の世界に帰るためよ\n私も改造した衣装を着てステージに立つわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.8629237489,
      "endTime": 108.836250718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、急に四人も増えて衣装作りは間に合うの？\n材料だって私達の分しか用意してないだろうし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.0629166282,
      "endTime": 117.6060682929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、今から追加で四人分の材料を確保するのは\n難しいかもしれないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.7962499615,
      "endTime": 124.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "momo",
      "speakerName": "モモ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-momo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-momo002.m4a",
      "text": "だったら、少ない材料でも作れる衣装に\nデザインを変更してみるのはどうですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.5652550377,
      "endTime": 131.6786014236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "モモちゃん、ナイスアイデアです！　衣装の布面積を\n半分に削れば五人分の材料で九人分作れますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.8652682619,
      "endTime": 141.141391118,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "衣装の布面積が半分に……\n冬なのにやたら肌の露出が多いサンタになりそうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.3319349286,
      "endTime": 149.35193471890003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_03-kyui004.m4a",
      "text": "は、肌の露出は抑えめにしてよ！？\nハレンチ禁止！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.5436351456,
      "endTime": 153.7667027787,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6556.364854399988
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7489.698187699986
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8756.364854400004
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――クリスマスライブ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.7000442501,
      "endTime": 155.8666915889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
